{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/blog/2019/10/25/policemain","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Kim Yoo seok' Blog","author":"Kim Yoo Seok","siteUrl":"https://yoolog.netlify.com"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"a2fe34f6-caad-5ebd-a2c7-3509b9c0b02e","excerpt":"개요 실내 실시간 공기질 측정 모니터링프로젝트를 마치고 얼마 안 지나서 사내에서 진행하는 프로젝트에\n투입되었다. 바로 경찰청 키오스크이다. 크게 4개의 메뉴로 나뉘는데 그 중 2개를 맡아서 하였다. \n공지사항, 매뉴얼/교육 메뉴인데 진행하면서 가장 핵심적인 기능은 PDF…","html":"<p>\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/327224e3ada6e12c97f5f9c6cf6041d4/caa67/policemain.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 489px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 64.41717791411043%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"policemain\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/327224e3ada6e12c97f5f9c6cf6041d4/caa67/policemain.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/327224e3ada6e12c97f5f9c6cf6041d4/cf440/policemain.png 148w,\n/static/327224e3ada6e12c97f5f9c6cf6041d4/d2d38/policemain.png 295w,\n/static/327224e3ada6e12c97f5f9c6cf6041d4/caa67/policemain.png 489w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 489px) 100vw, 489px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </p>\n<br>\n<br>\n<h1>개요</h1>\n<br>\n<p><strong>실내 실시간 공기질 측정 모니터링</strong>프로젝트를 마치고 얼마 안 지나서 사내에서 진행하는 프로젝트에\n투입되었다. 바로 <strong>경찰청 키오스크</strong>이다. 크게 4개의 메뉴로 나뉘는데 그 중 2개를 맡아서 하였다.\n공지사항, 매뉴얼/교육 메뉴인데 진행하면서 가장 핵심적인 기능은 <strong>PDF</strong>를 띄우는 일과 <strong>Video</strong>를\n재생하는 일이다. 또한 PDF는 한 페이지씩 보이며 <strong>검색을 통해</strong> 원하는 페이지로 바로 갈 수 있도록 하였다. 전부 처음하는 일이라 만만치 않은 작업이었다. 특히 <strong>라이브러리</strong>를 가져다 쓰는 일에서 수많은 시행착오를 겪으며 완성하였다.</p>\n<br>\n<br>\n<h1>기획</h1>\n<br> \n<ul>\n<li><strong>화면은</strong> 키오스크 해상도에 맞추어 모든 요소를 가변이 아닌 고정된 크기로 만든다.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/b149f8c258474c0567e5142cb663ad26/04655/main.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 431px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 145.4756380510441%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"main\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/b149f8c258474c0567e5142cb663ad26/04655/main.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/b149f8c258474c0567e5142cb663ad26/cf440/main.png 148w,\n/static/b149f8c258474c0567e5142cb663ad26/d2d38/main.png 295w,\n/static/b149f8c258474c0567e5142cb663ad26/04655/main.png 431w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 431px) 100vw, 431px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>공지사항</strong> 메뉴에서 PDF를 컴포넌트 단위로 최대 7개만 화면에 보이도록 한다.\n페이지네이션을 페이지를 나누고 초과되는 PDF는 오래된 순으로 다음 페이지에 추가된다.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/36648ceb404837ea5c180dab7f0fa11c/04655/notice.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 431px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 170.53364269141534%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"notice\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/36648ceb404837ea5c180dab7f0fa11c/04655/notice.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/36648ceb404837ea5c180dab7f0fa11c/cf440/notice.png 148w,\n/static/36648ceb404837ea5c180dab7f0fa11c/d2d38/notice.png 295w,\n/static/36648ceb404837ea5c180dab7f0fa11c/04655/notice.png 431w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 431px) 100vw, 431px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>PDF</strong>를 클릭 할 시 Modal형태로 해당 파일에 첫 페이지가 보인다. 양 옆에 버튼을 추가하여 한 장씩 넘어갈수 있도록 하고 페이지를 검색하여 원하는 페이지로 바로 이동도 가능하다.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/d4634d1b3dc1981a3417c1716c8da9bb/04655/pdf.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 431px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 143.85150812064964%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"pdf\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/d4634d1b3dc1981a3417c1716c8da9bb/04655/pdf.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/d4634d1b3dc1981a3417c1716c8da9bb/cf440/pdf.png 148w,\n/static/d4634d1b3dc1981a3417c1716c8da9bb/d2d38/pdf.png 295w,\n/static/d4634d1b3dc1981a3417c1716c8da9bb/04655/pdf.png 431w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 431px) 100vw, 431px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>비디오</strong>는 클릭 할 시 바로 재생이 되며 일시정지 및 원하는 시간으로 이동이 가능하다.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/16560fef9772efe75acae0e65664d7e4/04655/video.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 431px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 124.5939675174014%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"video\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/16560fef9772efe75acae0e65664d7e4/04655/video.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/16560fef9772efe75acae0e65664d7e4/cf440/video.png 148w,\n/static/16560fef9772efe75acae0e65664d7e4/d2d38/video.png 295w,\n/static/16560fef9772efe75acae0e65664d7e4/04655/video.png 431w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 431px) 100vw, 431px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </p>\n<br>\n<br>\n<h1>기술설계</h1>\n<br>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Pagination</strong>라이브러리를 활용해서 하단에 페이지네이션을 구현한다.</li>\n</ul>\n<br>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"renux\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-renux line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-renux\">    npm install --save react-paginate</code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<br>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"jsx\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-jsx line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-jsx\">    <span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> ReactPaginate <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">'react-paginate'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n    <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>ReactPaginate\n        pageLinkClassName<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token string\">'linkpage'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>     <span class=\"token comment\">// 각각의 페이지요소에 &lt;li> 태그 css 수정</span>\n        containerClassName<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token string\">'pagination'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>  <span class=\"token comment\">// 페이지네이션 전체 컨테이너 css 수정</span>\n        activeClassName<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token string\">'activepages'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>    <span class=\"token comment\">// 클릭하여 활성화 된 &lt;li> 태그 css 수정</span>\n        activeLinkClassName<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token string\">'activelink'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// 클릭하여 활성화 된 &lt;a> 태그 css 수정</span>\n        pageRangeDisplayed<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token number\">5</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>             <span class=\"token comment\">// 화면에 보일 페이지 수 조정</span>\n        pageCount<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token keyword\">this</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>state<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>current<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>     <span class=\"token comment\">// 현재 화면에 활성화 할 페이지 설정</span>\n        previousLabel<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>                    <span class=\"token comment\">// 이전으로 넘어가는 버튼 html 및 css</span>\n            <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>button</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">className</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">'</span>preBtn<span class=\"token punctuation\">'</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">\n                </span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>img</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">src</span><span class=\"token script language-javascript\"><span class=\"token script-punctuation punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>back<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">alt</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">'</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">/></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">\n            </span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>button</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n        nextLabel<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>                        <span class=\"token comment\">// 다음으로 넘어가는 버튼 html 및 css</span>\n            <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>button</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">className</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">'</span>nextBtn<span class=\"token punctuation\">'</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">\n                </span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>img</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">src</span><span class=\"token script language-javascript\"><span class=\"token script-punctuation punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>back<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">alt</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">'</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">className</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">'</span>nextBtnImg<span class=\"token punctuation\">'</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">/></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">\n            </span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>button</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n    <span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<br>\n<p>받아온 <strong>Paginate API</strong>를 해당 GitHub주소에서 어떻게 사용하고 내가 커스텀하기에 충분한 함수들이 구비되어있는지 확인한 후 필요한 함수를 사용해서 구현하였다. </p>\n<br>\n<p><em>참고링크 :</em> <strong><a href=\"https://github.com/AdeleD/react-paginate#readme\">https://github.com/AdeleD/react-paginate#readme</a></strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>PDF</strong>라이브러리를 활용해서 PDF창을 띄우는 작업을 진행하였다.</li>\n</ul>\n<br>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"renux\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-renux line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-renux\">    npm install --save react-pdf</code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<br>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"jsx\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-jsx line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-jsx\">    <span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> Document<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> Page<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> pdfjs <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"react-pdf\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n    <span class=\"token comment\">//react-pdf을 최신버전으로 업데이트</span>\n    pdfjs<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>GlobalWorkerOptions<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>workerSrc <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token string\">//cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/pdf.js/</span><span class=\"token interpolation\"><span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">${</span>pdfjs<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>version<span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">}</span></span><span class=\"token string\">/pdf.worker.js</span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n    <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>Document\n\n        <span class=\"token comment\">//활용 함수들</span>\n\n        file            <span class=\"token comment\">// 활성화 할 PDF 설정</span>\n        onLoadSuccess   <span class=\"token comment\">// PDF가 성공적으로 활성화 됬을 때 콜백되는 함수</span>\n        loading         <span class=\"token comment\">// 로딩중일 때 콜백되는 함수</span>\n    <span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n        <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>Page\n\n            <span class=\"token comment\">//활용 함수들</span>\n\n            width   <span class=\"token comment\">// 넓이 설정</span>\n            height  <span class=\"token comment\">// 높이 설정</span>\n            loading <span class=\"token comment\">// 로딩중일 때 콜백되는 함수</span>\n            noData  <span class=\"token comment\">// 활성화 할 PDF가 없을 때 콜백되는 함수</span>\n            error   <span class=\"token comment\">// \"Failed to load the page.\"이 발생하면 콜백되는 함수</span>\n        <span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span><span class=\"token class-name\">Document</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>   </code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<br>\n<p><strong>사용한 PDF</strong>라이브러리가 유지보수가 안되어 있어서 제작자가 이 API를 만들면서 사용한 <strong>Mozilla</strong>에서 제공하는 <em>javascript pdf</em>라이브러리가 최선버전이 아니었다. 이 때문에 화면에서 pdf의 화면이 모두 깨져서 나왔다. <strong>node_modules</strong>에서 이 라이브러리 폴더에 접근 후 원본을 수정하여 <strong>Mozilla</strong>에서 제공하는 <em>javascript pdf</em>라이브러리만 따로 최신버전으로 업데이트하는 작업을 진행하였다. </p>\n<br>\n<p><em>참고링크 :</em> <strong><a href=\"https://github.com/wojtekmaj/react-pdf#readme\">https://github.com/wojtekmaj/react-pdf#readme</a></strong></p>\n<br>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Video</strong>라이브러리를 활용하여 영상 재생을 구현한다.</li>\n</ul>\n<br>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"renux\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-renux line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-renux\">    npm install --save video-react</code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<br>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"jsx\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-jsx line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-jsx\">    <span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>Player<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">'video-react'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n    <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>Player\n        autoPlay    <span class=\"token comment\">// 영상 자동재생 여부 Type : boolean</span>\n        src         <span class=\"token comment\">// 재생 할 비디오 설정</span>\n    <span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<br>\n<p><strong>video-react 라이브러리</strong> 해당 GitHub에 들어가서 필요한 함수 및 제공하는 컴포넌트를 활용해 구현하였다.  </p>\n<br>\n<p><em>참고링크 :</em> <strong><a href=\"https://video-react.js.org/components/player/\">https://video-react.js.org/components/player/</a></strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Dependancies</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"jsx\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-jsx line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-jsx\">    <span class=\"token string\">\"dependencies\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        <span class=\"token string\">\"video-react\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"^0.14.1\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n        <span class=\"token string\">\"react-modal\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"^3.10.1\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n        <span class=\"token string\">\"react-paginate\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"^6.3.0\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n        <span class=\"token string\">\"react-pdf\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"^4.1.0\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n        <span class=\"token string\">\"react-pdf-js\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"^5.1.0\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n        <span class=\"token string\">\"@material-ui/core\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"^4.5.0\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n        <span class=\"token string\">\"@react-pdf/renderer\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"^1.6.6\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n        <span class=\"token string\">\"@react-pdf/styled-components\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"^1.4.0\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n        <span class=\"token string\">\"rc-pagination\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token 